Setup
-----

install isync notmuch

1. Insert passwords in ~/.mailpass-<account_name>.gpg
2. ln -s ~/src/emacs.d/mail/conf/mbsyncrc ~/.mbsyncrc && chmod 600 ~/.mbsyncrc
3. ln -s ~/src/emacs.d/mail/conf/notmuch-config ~/.notmuch-config && chmod 600 ~/.notmuch-config
4. ln -s ~/src/emacs.d/mail/lisp/90-notmuch.el ~/src/emacs.d/lisp/enabled/90-notmuch.el
5. ln -s ~/src/emacs.d/mail/bin/mailfetcher ~/bin/mailfetcher && chmod 700 ~/bin/mailfetcher

Run
---

mailfetcher





BUGS & feats
------------
- multiple account
- SMTP setup





